channel.title: Clients
channel.description:
ok,well i have project czar base source,and i use the galkons client for my server,which it works really well with,BUT a few items are "nulled" and can't be seen or used,and also when i try to use prayer on the client it disconnects the client,i have prayer on my server but the client doesn't support it,so i was wondering is there a client that works perfect with czar source,or is there a client that works with all sources and doesn't nulled anything out,if so can you send me link for it,thanks
~cody

item.title: Clients
item.dc:creator: @gamma gamma
item.description:
@gamma wrote:

czar base sourc has silab item ID’s, and galkons client has its own id’s.

go into class8.java, and search the item that is nulled, and at the top of the search you should see the item id.
change that ID to the silab 1
